description:
SAVE THE DATE!!!!!

If you have something to share, we need speakers for this event (and for future events too!). Remember, not all talks require you to be the world's leading expert on your topic - real-world learning stories are also REALLY helpful to our community. We're very supportive of first time speakers too. Go on! You know you want to! Just get in touch with one of the organisers via Meetup or chat with one of our organisers at an event.
title: Elastic March
